        "description": {
            "value": "<p><strong>Activate</strong> <span class=\"pf2-icon\">2</span> Interact</p>\n<p>This magnetized suit is strapped to your body over your armor or clothes. When you Activate it, you must choose whether to set it to attract or repel.</p>\n<p>While set to attract, you take a -1 item penalty to your AC against attacks made by metal weapons, while creatures within a @Template[type:emanation|distance:5] other than you gain a +1 item bonus to their AC. If set to repel, you gain a +1 item bonus to AC against attacks made with metal weapons. While attracting metal, you gain a +1 item bonus to Athletics checks to @Compendium[pf2e.actionspf2e.Climb]{Climb} metal objects and @Compendium[pf2e.actionspf2e.Grapple]{Grapple} metal creatures and a -1 item penalty to Athletics checks to @Compendium[pf2e.actionspf2e.Shove]{Shove} metal creatures. While repelling metal, you gain a +1 item bonus to Athletics checks to Shove metal creatures, but you take a -1 item penalty to Climb metal objects and Grapple metal creatures.</p>"
